"------------------------------------------------
" 新規Windowを開く際の設定
"------------------------------------------------
" 新規windowを右側に開く
map <C-w><C-v> :bel vnew<CR>:VimFiler .<CR>
"map <C-w><C-v> :Vexplore! .<CR>
"map! <C-w><C-v> <Esc>:Vexplore!<CR>
" 新規windowを下側に開く
set splitbelow
map <C-w><C-h> :bel new<CR>:VimFiler .<CR>
"map <C-w><C-h> :Hexplore .<CR>
"map! <C-w><C-h> <Esc>:Hexplore<CR>
